{"word":"ἀστυγείτων","slug":"ἀστυγείτων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀστυγείτων</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:genitive'>gen.</a> <el>ονος</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>near</i> or <i>bordering on a city</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>as <a href='S:Substantive'>Subst.</a> <i>a neighbour to the city, a borderer</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}